description: Chau Philomene One is one of four families within the Chau superfamily. He is hardy, ideal for headings and highlighted text. His narrow letters and sharp angles give him a distinctive personality. Chau Philomene One is a Unicode typeface family that supports languages that use the Latin script and its variants, and could be expanded to support other scripts. To contribute to the project contact Vicente Lamonaca at TipoType.
